      <hedline>
        <hl1>A Classic Improved</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By JULIE V. IOVINE</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Iovine, Julie V</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Psychedelic Fluidium lamp is designed by Ross Lovegrove for Mathmos, British company; hoto (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Nothing could be groovier than a lava lamp, that 60's icon of the psychedelic slo-mo lane. Except perhaps, a Fluidium lamp, right, around $125. This updated edition is designed by Ross Lovegrove for Mathmos, the British company that produces the original Astro lamp. Mr. Lovegrove, known for the sensual curves in his designs, went high tech, using new heatproof plastics and making the colored ooze match its container. Fly to London to buy the lamp, or look for it in the States soon.</p>
        <p>JULIE V. IOVINE</p>
      </block>
